title: 'Disable the ftpd_use_passive_mode SELinux Boolean'

description: |-
    By default, the SELinux boolean <tt>ftpd_use_passive_mode</tt> is disabled.
    If this setting is enabled, it should be disabled.
    <sebool-macro enable="false" sebool="ftpd_use_passive_mode" />

